<speech>
"Now you must find your way to Grin’s Crag.
Remember your task. Do hot stray from it, for your
enemies are too numerous. When you have passed
Grin’s Crag you will reach a giant wooden door
leading to Kellar’s Keep. Once opened, you will be
able to lead the Emperor and his army back to
